Title: Page 1
Description.note: 4 leaves : paper ; 211 x 153 mm. Credit section of an accounting record, probably of a religious society dedicated to the rosary. Includes charitable donations, including gifts of livestock and money. Leaf count does not include cover sheet. Text in Spanish and Nahuatl.
